<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Role Change Notification</title>
</head>

<body
  style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 20px;">
        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
                style="background-color: #000; width: 100%; text-align: center;">
                <tr>
                  <td
                    style="color: #fff; padding: 10px; margin: 0; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-weight: bold; font-size: 24px;">
                    ://AuthN</td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <h2 style="color: #000; font-size: 20px;">Account Role Update</h2>
              <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
              <p>Your account role has been updated. Your new role is <strong>{{newRole}}</strong></p>
              <p>You can log in to view the changes to your account by clicking the button below:</p>
              <p>
                <a href="{{link}}"
                  style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #000; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">View
                  My Account</a>
              </p>
              <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can also copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
              <p style="word-break: break-all;">{{link}}</p>
              <p>If you did not request this change or believe it was made in error, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
              <p>Best regards,<br><span
                  style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-weight: bold;">://AuthN</span></p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin-top: 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
        <p>This email was sent to {{email}}. If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>